{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_01_02",
  "title": "兵藤雫 2話 沢山のファンレター",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "これはさくら宛で、これは怜……\nこっちは千紗、遙子さんのが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These are for Sakura‚ and these are for Rei…\nThese for Chisa‚ and these for Haruko…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.630498933792114,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4330.498933792119,
          "startTime": 8.960997867584233
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れさま……です\nレッスン室、戸締まり……してきた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you…for doing that.\nI’ve locked the lesson room's… door.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.95899793624878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、雫\nそれじゃあぼちぼち寮に戻ろうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Shizuku.\nShall we head back to the dorm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.220088952237912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "それは……手紙？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are those… letters?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.31099801063538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そう、サニーピースのみんなに届いたファンレターだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ the fan letters to all the members of Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.072267818450932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "結構、たくさん……\n私のも……ある？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are a lot of them.\nAre there… any for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.16881299579845,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、もちろん\nまだこっちの山の中にも眠ってると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ of course.\nI think they’re still hiding in this pile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.52983821108939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ……私も……\n仕分け、手伝ってもいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case…\nCan I help with‚ the sorting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.685402199150886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、助かるよ。じゃあ、内容の確認は済んでるから\n宛先ごとに分けてくれるかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’d be a great help. The content has been checked‚\nso please sort them by recipient.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.37749598068105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "ん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.17093790372214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "……これが最後の一枚\n誰宛の、ファンレターか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…This is the last one.\nWho is this fan letter to?…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.07093790372213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "私は……私宛に、一票",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I bet… it’s for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1823831440746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それ、こっちが他に賭け辛いんだが……\nじゃあ……そうじゃない方に一票！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re making it hard for me. I’d have to pick someone.\nLet’s see… I’ll bet it’s not for you instead!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.80211093045666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "ん、では……オープン",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I’ll open it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.21675937342042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "やった、私の勝ち……\nついでに、仕分けも終了……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I win…\nAnd the sorting’s also done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.78342604008708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。最終的には宛先当てゲームになったけど……\n手伝ってくれてありがとう、雫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. It turned into a recipient guessing game at the end‚\nbut thanks for helping me‚ Shizuku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1797271333743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "……ううん\n私も……気になってた、から",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Nah…\nI was… curious‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.45135111162232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "ファンレター……私宛の、内容\n早く読みたくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I wanted to read my fan letter…\nstraight away…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.45993253538175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことか\nなら、ここで少し読んでいくか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nSo‚ would you like to read some here first?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.35791829229728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "……ううん\n寮に帰るまで、取っておく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Nah…\nI’ll take them with me until I get back to the dorm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.37458941109227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "多分、今、ここで読んだら……\n泣いちゃうと、思うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I read it here‚\nI think I might cry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1294674963596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "……ずっと、ファンレター……\n出す側、だったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I was always the one\nsending fan letters‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.93613416302625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "アイドル、始めて……\nもらえただけでも、びっくり、なのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so getting one for the first time…\nas an idol is a surprise…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.68144622212468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、嬉しくて……がんばってきて、よかった\nそんな風に、思うから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but I’m happy… I’m glad I kept trying.\nFeeling like that‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.014779555458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "中を、読んだら……きっと、我慢できない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t be able to hold back… my tears after reading what’s in it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.18955249951105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（雫の声は少し震えていた。ファンレターをもらう）\n（ことがどれほど嬉しいのか、俺には想像も付かない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Shizuku’s voice was trembling a little. I can’t imagine)\n(how happy she must be to get a fan letter.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.97274999783247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、早く寮に帰ろうか\n……読んでみたいんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So shall we get back to the dorm quickly?\n…You want to read it‚ don’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.17274999783257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "…………うん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.1858643226751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_way-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_noon",
      "startTime": 154.4191976560085
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "……ファンレター、もらって\n思ったこと……ある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Getting a fan letter\nmade me think…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.9858643226751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_01_02-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "ファンレターって……とっても\n勇気づけられるもの、だったんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought getting a fan letter…\nis something… that really encourages you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.0352336188357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
